/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a bustling street scene in Beijing, China. The vantage point is from a high angle, providing a bird's eye view of the urban landscape. The street, lined with lush green trees and towering buildings, stretches out into the distance. The buildings, predominantly white and gray, rise high into the clear blue sky, their glass facades reflecting the sunlight. The sun, positioned in the top right corner of the image, casts a bright light that illuminates the scene, highlighting the stark contrast between the natural and man-made elements. Despite the absence of people in the frame, the image conveys a sense of life and activity, characteristic of a busy city street.
